{"tid":1463384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警嫁禍集中post 救手足新方向， 搜證組","createTime":"2019-08-13T12:54:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T13:11:07.000Z","uid":240555,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4c31fea904eab66b5efa0d363cedffdc02c003b1","tid":1463384,"uid":240555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:54:50.000Z","msg":"<ins><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ApUNHU8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FApUNHU8.jpg&h=f09aca8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mf09bOC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMf09bOC.jpg&h=39cea8f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tghb9Aw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTghb9Aw.jpg&h=c5e53f68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yjUNHVJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyjUNHVJ.jpg&h=31b5fadd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日我見到好多消息，對唔住我只係貼左一部分內容。<br />\n希望大家都可以幫手fact check.. <br />\n警察所有暴動罪行嘅定性，同埋武力升級全部都會變成不合理。啲畫面甚至可以叫做假新聞，全香港人都變哂理解錯畫面，手足畀人嫁禍。警察分信力完全係零，仲要近乎全部罪行都係警察包攬。<br />\n<br />\n。。有啲野番唔到轉頭，大家嘅傷勢，義士嘅生命唔多唔少係因警察制造嘅假畫面令政府藉口去轉移視視，拒絕五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以開post, tg group, 去從新聞畫面/網上圖片去搵番證據出黎。<br />\n<br />\n還香港人一個清白，至少完成五大訴求裡面三樣。<br />\n<br />\n釋放義士<br />\n撤銷暴動定性<br />\n成立獨立委員會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4d3260a622bf02083752a021d41840bbc91cf3","tid":1463384,"uid":240555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:55:59.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"d107ac23276c72a4519e2409355f4abb450f0eb8","tid":1463384,"uid":240555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T1